          "source": "第二部分  模块二  第四节 焊接技术及电路组装调试",
          "year": 2025,
          "difficulty": 0.4,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如下图所示的直流稳压电源的焊接电路图。试：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/1/10/3667080712544256/3667232590741504/STEM/abb58641605a47ea9fb38eda7fb01a53.png\" width=\"439\" height=\"132\" /></p><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（1）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将未接入的元件补画完整；</span></div></div><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">元器件安装正确无误后，在变压器一次侧接</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">220V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">交流电、测量</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">AB</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、负载</span><math latex=\"$R_{\\mathrm{L}}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mtext>L</mtext></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两端的电压应将万用表分别置于何档？若将可调电阻</span><math latex=\"$R_{1}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">置于</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">480</span><math latex=\"$\\Upomega$\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">AB</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><math latex=\"$R_{\\mathrm{L}}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mtext>L</mtext></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两端的电压是多少？</span></div></div><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（3）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">说明电解电容</span><math latex=\"$\\mathrm{C}_{1}$\"><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><math latex=\"$\\mathrm{C}_{3}$\"><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的最小耐压值；</span></div></div><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（4）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">说明电容</span><math latex=\"$\\mathrm{C}_{2}$\"><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的作用；</span></div></div><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（5）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">若用万用表测得</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">AB</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两端的电压只有</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">20V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，说明电路中各元件是否正常，若不正常，请找出故障元件，此时负载</span><math latex=\"$R_{\\mathrm{L}}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mtext>L</mtext></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两端的电压怎样变化？</span></div></div></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\">（1）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/1/10/3667080712544256/3667232590741504/ANSWER/0d7a5670628a4eae9e96732839f3bef8.png\" width=\"395\" height=\"112\" /></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（2）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直流电压档，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">24V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">6.25V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（3）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">28.28V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">16.5V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（4）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><math latex=\"$\\mathrm{C}_{2}$\"><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可消除</span><math latex=\"$R_{\\mathrm{P}}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mtext>P</mtext></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上的纹波电压，使取样电压稳定。</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（5）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一只二极管或对臂的两只二极管开路。</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>",
