          "paperId": "3875266665897984",
          "source": "《电工技术模块》直流电路-知识点训练卷 2026版湖南省电工电子类专业 考纲百套卷 第8卷",
          "year": 2025,
          "difficulty": 0.45,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如下图所示，已知</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">U</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>s1</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=15V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">U</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>s2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=4V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">U</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>s3</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">;=13V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>1</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>3</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>4</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> =1Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>5</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">=9Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/10/31/3875266665897984/3881871378096128/STEM/d2d8ffc3519d4b589e09235beed42e40.png\" width=\"271\" height=\"157\" /></p><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（1）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当开关</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">S</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">断开时，试求电阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>5</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上的电压</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">U</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>5</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，和电流</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">I</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>5</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">;</span></div></div><div class=\"qml-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><div class=\"qml-stem\"><span class=\"ques-no\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当开关</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">S</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">闭合时，试用戴维南定理计算</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">I</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><sub>5</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></div></div></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\">（1）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当开关</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">S</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">断开时：</span><math latex=\"$l_{5}=0\\left(A\\right)$\"><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\"><mi>A</mi></mfenced></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span><math latex=\"$U_{5}=I_{5}\\times R_{5}=0\\times 9=0\\left(V\\right)$\"><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\"><mi>V</mi></mfenced></mrow></math></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（2）<span class=\"qml-an-sq\" id-container=\"question\"><span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当开关</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">S</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">闭合时：</span><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∵</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/10/31/3875266665897984/3881871378096128/ANSWER/f2c25067b726429da7f49c4dfd4257ab.png\" width=\"324\" height=\"75\" /><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/10/31/3875266665897984/3881871378096128/ANSWER/b576c5a4f9c44ba58fa0890da9843da2.png\" width=\"121\" height=\"151\" /></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2025/10/31/3875266665897984/3881871378096128/ANSWER/2200560381ce4fc181d73e7c084a68b4.png\" width=\"306\" height=\"78\" /></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∴</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><math latex=\"$U_{5}=U_{a}-U_{b}=\\frac{19}{2}-\\frac{13}{2}=\\frac{6}{2}=3\\left(V\\right)$\"><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mi>a</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mi>b</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>19</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>13</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\"><mi>V</mi></mfenced></mrow></math></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><math latex=\"$R_{ab}=1//1+1//1=0.5+0.5=1\\left(\\Omega \\right)$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mo>/</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mo>/</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></mfenced></mrow></math></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∴</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><math latex=\"$l_{5}=\\frac{3}{1+9}=\\frac{3}{10}=0.3\\left(A\\right)$\"><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.3</mn><mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\"><mi>A</mi></mfenced></mrow></math></p></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>",
